{"tid":1822900,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"桃田賢斗遇車禍受傷 司機當場死亡","createTime":"2020-01-13T08:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T02:32:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"144f8d119e1e4021f3329439a7ddb8a202315737","tid":1822900,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T08:46:16.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】剛剛贏得馬來西亞羽毛球大師賽男單冠軍的日本球手桃田賢斗，回程時遇車禍受傷，司機則當場死亡。<br />\n<br />\n桃田賢斗和三位團隊成員於星期一凌晨前往機場時，乘坐的客貨車撞上前面的貨車，車頭嚴重損毀，司機當場死亡。桃田賢斗據報鼻骨骨折，面部亦有割傷，同車的三人受輕傷。<br />\n<br />\n25歲的桃田賢斗剛剛於馬來西亞大師賽擊敗丹麥的艾素臣贏得冠軍，暫時未知事件對他備戰東京奧運有多大影響。"},{"pid":"b6751252a6ca8d514a3e689a5c252b1dcdf081f3","tid":1822900,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T08:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f712d013793c22e8edde4613cdbaea9d542f03","tid":1822900,"uid":188311,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T08:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5886130fa261d50b23a6dd7c6a44eaab7a7e25","tid":1822900,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T08:51:06.000Z","msg":"東京奧運金牌大熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c842ac543d9f171376fe1c042a5105a995c25125","tid":1822900,"uid":188311,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"5f5886130fa261d50b23a6dd7c6a44eaab7a7e25","tid":1822900,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T08:51:06.000Z","msg":"東京奧運金牌大熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fro